Description:
   Binding Strike is a precise, targeted attack that hampers the opponent's
   ability to move freely. The Sentinel exploits openings in the target's
   defenses, striking joints, tendons, or pressure points to reduce their
   mobility. The target's movement and evasion are impaired for the duration
   of the effect.

   Binding Strike deals physical damage in addition to applying the movement
   debuff. It synergizes well with other Sentinel techniques that rely on
   catching a hindered opponent, such as Verdict and Ninth Descent. The
   impairment affects flee attempts and dodge chances.
